Transcription.Text: Coming around the great mass of the Chateau Laurier, he braked to a screeching stop. A flying saucer was tilting and dipping over the war memorial. There was a deep whirring sound, and a high-pitched hissing overtone that sang in his ears with an almost painful sharpness.
